---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="ABOUT" description="About Bård Ionson — AI artist, NFT pioneer, and creator of SAGE Anomaly">
  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-img">
      <img src="/images/promoDropImage.jpg" alt="SAGE Anomaly promotional image" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <span class="tag">// THE ARTIST</span>
      <h1>BÅRD<br/>IONSON</h1>
      <div class="bio terminal-block">
        <p>
          Bård Ionson has been creating art since 2012. In 2018, SuperRare accepted him
          to display art on their platform — one of the earliest crypto art galleries.
        </p>
        <p>
          The SAGE Anomaly project began as an exploration of the real SAGE computer network —
          the Cold War-era missile defense system that stretched across North America.
          The historical reality became the seed of a fiction: what if the network had
          detected something that wasn't Soviet?
        </p>
        <p>
          Working with <strong>DCGAN models trained on oscilloscope art</strong>, evolved through
          StyleGAN and Pix2Pix image-to-image translation, Bård built a visual language for
          the Entity — an artificial intelligence that exists outside human time.
        </p>
        <p>
          The artwork lives on Async.art as a programmable multi-edition piece —
          303 unique probes, 16 layers, 380,436 combinations — and on SuperRare and KnownOrigin.
          The written story is released in parallel, chapter by chapter.
        </p>
        <p>
          The novel is ongoing. The Entity is still transmitting.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://async.art/v2/482?referrer=masters" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span>ASYNC.ART — ARTIFICIAL ENTITY PROBES</span><span>↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://superrare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span>SUPERRARE</span><span>↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://knownorigin.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span>KNOWNORIGIN</span><span>↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://bardionson.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span>BÅRD IONSON STUDIO</span><span>↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://bardsfreakyfaces.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span>BARD'S FREAKY FACES</span><span>↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
  }

  .about-img {
    overflow: hidden;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
  }

  .about-img img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: saturate(0.3) contrast(1.1);
  }

  .about-text {
    padding: 5rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .link-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .link-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .link-item:hover { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.03); color: var(--green); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-img { position: static; height: 50vw; min-height: 250px; }
    .about-text { padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
